Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:15.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:20.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
